{"tid":1432152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【承上題】＋15史詩的積極的進擊的街招文宣策略","createTime":"2019-08-08T07:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T12:20:37.000Z","uid":265197,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"20acfdac9250f0658e1a8ac6858a2da7bca5b6be","tid":1432152,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:22:22.000Z","msg":"承上題<br />\n<br />\n極嚴重!!發覺文宣有個好大獲嘅問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431648</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n文宣組唔一定會識點樣用最煽情嘅方式去表達<br />\n呢個世界8成以上都係老實人<br />\n剩低有部分人係完全廢up<br />\n明知句句廢話句句假話都可以眼都唔眨一下咁講出口<br />\n就好似d高官同呢個野咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/USBvH8S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUSBvH8S.jpg&h=4bb42af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地轉數比佢地快<br />\n就要玩得比佢地叻<br />\n係呢d灰色地帶中間遊走<br />\n<br />\n舉個例<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3RsE0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3RsE0.jpg&h=614e33f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藍營果邊係完全唔理真相咁去亂作老屈<br />\n咁呢d比d開始想覺醒嘅市民一查就會即刻穿煲<br />\n呢個亦係比低lv平民吸收exp練功場所<br />\n<br />\n我地要做嘅就係根據事實無限量煲大<br />\n你出新聞稿就話要持平姐<br />\n而家人地打爛仔交你仲講咁多規矩<br />\n<br />\n文字係非常有力量嘅野<br />\n我地點解會有人支持<br />\n因為我地有正當性<br />\n我地行使緊應有嘅公民權利<br />\n我地對抗緊不義嘅條例<br />\n<br />\n同樣地對家而家用暴徒去形容示威者<br />\n用執法去蓋過警察濫權<br />\n用反暴力去掩飾政府冷處理迫到民眾行動升級嘅問題<br />\n如同用幾支釘釘實我地標籤我地<br />\n咁民意慢慢就會自然咁歸邊<br />\n令人覺得我唔暴力所以呢d野我就應該唔支持<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GOo2zo2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGOo2zo2.jpg&h=64aea3f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似天水圍少女咁<br />\n對家打執法牌<br />\n拎左個正當性咁就會令人覺得我地做乜都係自己攞黎<br />\n點樣寫可以去令人覺得有唔妥呢?<br />\n<br />\n男性警員拘捕期間<span style=\"color: red;\">脫下少女內褲</span><br />\n令少女下陰<span style=\"color: red;\">曝露</span>於公眾面前<br />\n並<span style=\"color: red;\">拒絕</span>讓少女穿回<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">這仍是<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">執法</span></span>嗎?</span><br />\n如此<span style=\"color: red;\">禽獸</span>行為，你<span style=\"color: red;\">支持</span>嗎?<br />\n<br />\n咁樣一睇你會考慮嘅唔係佢點解甩底褲<br />\n而係呢樣係咪仲係屬於執法呢?<br />\n只要將警員執法維持治安呢點抹去<br />\n市民就會好快從另一個角色去睇唔同嘅野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要記住!!<br />\n我地唔係做公司文件唔係做合約!!<br />\n只要唔好做假新聞<br />\n你煽情係無人會理你<br />\n因為每張可能人地只係望幾秒<br />\n要用標題去吸引更多人去留意<br />\n我地係做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">貼!!街!!招!!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地做緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">八 掛 新 聞</span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">詳細技巧希望有記者或者報紙佬可以幫手傳授下技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n小弟劣po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求有更加多有學識之士幫手諗諗"},{"pid":"7ef22f220b96d1ae8f263d13e8eb7e12e0c88e81","tid":1432152,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:23:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0430472ba7ffcec3b1ec9df9eb8b81ab5b90fc4","tid":1432152,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:24:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"194e7dc943f396bd8ba0f0d8e6013c37cb3f9282","tid":1432152,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:26:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d05188fb01b279a6f2ae172e2ddc68354f6dcc","tid":1432152,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e990b0fe374f8f21e2a013149bfe73